 rs\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    @taraka: Glad you're stepping up to tell everyone what is necessary and what is unnecessary. What would we do without people like you. While we're at banning stuff, let's ban freedom of choice too, because taraka here can obviously choose what's better for us better than we can.\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Haha hi5 Ispangee! Taraka, we are proud of you :p\n                                            "], "contact": "Call 0114345253", "address": "No. 545A, Madiwela Road, Thalawathugoda ", "directions": "It is at the intersection between Japan Friendship road and Thalawathugoda road (on your left you'll see a lit up Kandos balloon).", "opening_days": ["MONDAY", "TUESDAY", "WEDNESDAY", "THURSDAY", "FRIDAY", "SATURDAY", "SUNDAY"], "opening_hours": ["03:00 PM \u2013 08:00 PM", "03:00 PM \u2013 08:00 PM", "03:00 PM \u2013 08:00 PM", "03:00 PM \u2013 08:00 PM", "03:00 PM \u2013 08:00 PM", "03:00 PM \u2013 08:00 PM", "03:00 PM \u2013 08:00 PM"], "cuisine": ["Sri Lankan"], "price_range": "Between Rs. 200 - Rs. 500", "dishes": ["Kottu"], "overall_rating": "2", "quality_rating": "3", "service_rating": "2", "ambience_rating": "3", "near_by_places_names": ["Chasis", "Rasembula", "Atrium Restaurant ", "Samanala Restaurant", "Spinner"], "near_by_places_addresses": ["571/3Madiwela road,Thalawathugoda", "Kimbulawala junction,Pitakotte road\r\nMadiwela", "571/3, Madiwela Road, Thalawathugoda", "Pitakotte - Talawatugoda Rd, Sri Jayawardenepura, Kotte", "479, Thalawatugoda Road, Kibulawela, Madiwela"], "near_by_places_distances": [" 199 m away", " 221 m away", " 223 m away", " 275 m away", " 313 m away"], "similar_places": ["\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0da9\u0dd2 Food (Pelawatta)", "Rolex Hotel"]}
{"url": "https://www.yamu.lk/place/himsara-foods/review-15625", "name": "Himsara Foods", "excerpt": "A great place to grab some good rice and curry, along with a killer pork curry.", "yamu_review": ["\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                    Himsara is an average buth kade which only stands out for serving pork curry.\n                                                                                                                            ", "\n                                                                                                                                    ", "\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                    \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dba\u0dd2, \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0db8 \u0db1\u0dd6\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dd0\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dca. \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dcf \u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dca\u0db6\u0dd9 \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd9. \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dca\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca \u0d89\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dad\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0d9a, \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dcf \u0db6\u0dcf\u0dba\u0dd2...!\n                                                                                                                            ", "\n                                                                                                                                    ", "\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                    \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dbb \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0db6\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0da9\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca. \u0d92 \u0d9c\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc3 \u0dad\u0db8\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0d8c\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0d91\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0d91\u0d9a.\n                                                                                                                            "], "user_reviews": [], "user_comments": ["\n\n                                    Try the pork curry at Bakeps on the Narahenpita road, Also at B-leaf on the Boralesgamuwa road. Both rock.\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    I used to study at J-school which was right in front of Himsara. While the food was okay, there was one incident where a fellow student found maggots or a worm in his rice packet. There was also the incident where Himsara took on a contract for the cops to provide lunch packets for some event, and a group of them got food poisoning.\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Shanuki (or anyone in the know), is this B-leaf on the 120 route, Boralesgamuwa?\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Where exactly is Bakeps on the Narahenpita road?\n                                            "], "contact": null, "address": "7 Chitra Lane, Colombo 5 ", "directions": "From Thimbirigasaya go either past Fife Road (heading east/out) or past Torrington (heading west). Kirula Road is the next big road. Himsara is near the corner.", "opening_days": ["MONDAY", "TUESDAY", "WEDNESDAY", "THURSDAY", "FRIDAY", "SATURDAY", "SUNDAY"], "opening_hours": ["07:00 AM \u2013 09:00 PM", "07:00 AM \u2013 09:00 PM", "07:00 AM \u2013 09:00 PM", "07:00 AM \u2013 09:00 PM", "07:00 AM \u2013 09:00 PM", "07:00 AM \u2013 09:00 PM", "07:00 AM \u2013 09:00 PM"], "cuisine": ["Sri Lankan"], "price_range": "Less than 200", "dishes": ["Rice And Curry", "Pork"], "overall_rating": "2", "quality_rating": "2", "service_rating": "2", "ambience_rating": "2", "near_by_places_names": ["Fresheta", "Randoli Sports Club", "The Store", "Caf\u00e9 Noir Blanc", "Anim8"], "near_by_places_addresses": ["1, Chithra Lane, Colombo 05", "88, Kirula Road, Colombo 05", "27, Pathiba Road, Colombo 5", "No. 216, Rev. Muruththettuwe Ananda Nahimi Mawatha, Colombo 5", "232 Thimbirigasyaya Road, Colombo 5"], "near_by_places_distances": [" 78 m away", " 103 m away", " 137 m away", " 171 m away", " 181 m away"], "similar_places": ["Thulasi Hotel (Badulla)", "Rasembula"]}
{"url": "https://www.yamu.lk/place/dinemore-kohuwala/review-15783", "name": "Dinemore (Kohuwala) ", "excerpt": "Sri Lanka\u2019s favourite submarine is probably that at Dinemore. This fast food franchise has been around for quite a while, and by the looks of it they\u2019ve expanded and opened up many more restaurants in Colombo, Kandy and even expanding internationally by branching out into the beautiful islands of the Maldives.\r\n", "yamu_review": ["\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                    Sri Lanka\u2019s favourite submarine is probably that at Dinemore. This fast food franchise has been around for quite a while, and by the looks of it they\u2019ve expanded and opened up many more restaurants in Colombo, Kandy and even expanding internationally by branching out into the beautiful islands of the Maldives.\r\n\n                                                                                                                            ", "\n                                                                                                                                    ", "\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                    \u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3 \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc4\u0ddc\u0db3\u0db8 \u0dc3\u0db6\u0dca\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dda \u0da9\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0db8\u0ddd \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db4\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca.  \u0db8\u0dda \u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dab\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0d86\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbd\u0d9a \u0db4\u0da7\u0db1\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf. \u0d94\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dc4\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dda \u0db4\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0dad\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf. \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc5\u0db9 \u0db4\u0db8\u0dab\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dca \u0dad\u0dc0 \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0d85\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd8\u0dad \u0d9a\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dcf. \u0daf\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dca \u0d94\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dc4\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dbb \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dcf. \n                                                                                                                            "], "user_reviews": [], "user_comments": ["\n\n                                    There is a minimum amount of order to be available to deliver. There should be atleast two subs to qualify for a delivery. And also there is a delivery charge I can't remember how much. It should come around 80.\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    There web site indicate that they are delivering colombo 01-15 and they it turned out that it will be delivered only if you are in the main roads. \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Food poisoning - EVERY SINGLE TIME\u2026 I stay away from ALL Dinemores\u2026 I've tried 3 of them and it doesn't help\u2026\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    BT,I think it is your personal issue.\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    okay food but value for money\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Food Poisoning. i agree with BT. there food is shit. \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Absolute zero food poisoning\u2026best submarines i've ever had\u2026\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Best subs Ive ever had\u2026\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    What a service! I was trying to place a order today, i called the delivery number and it was utter ringing and no response, then i called the Dharmapala Branch\" and person who answered told me that \" Yeah the hotline people must be busy so because of that they wont answer the phone\" (Wow Dinamore what a great service!) Then he gave me another number saying that they will make the delivery so the number he gave me was 0112302702 when i called them No, you have to call the other number then they gave me 0115991991, at last ! i was so delight to hear the ringing tone but no answer but i didnt give up i called them again. Then one person answered with broken English and got the order who doesnt know name and Place he keep on repeating NAME NAME which i informed them Twice and the order took more than an hour :D Fabulous JOB!\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Cheap and good.", "\nAs they say-", "\nSo Much For So Little.", "\nI really enjoy Dinemore- The environment, Taste, Price, Salads, Beaf Chops, etc.,\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Delivery is an absolute disappointment! I got the delivery after 2 1/2 hours after much complaining. Once the delivery arrived I realized that I got the wrong order (1 chicken burger, I submarine and garlic bread became 2 submarines). Food was soggy! The person who took the order was not at all enthusiastic or alert, felt as if I was speaking to a DEAD body! The delivery boy failed to even ask proper directions but hangs up soon. So many excuses!!! Customer service is a BIG NEGATIVE! \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Never answer there hotline when you need food -.- I would rather Oder KFC\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Other branches are ok but this Kohuwala branch is good for nothing and should be closed. unclean plus thier service sux. Everytinme i have ordered a chicken burger they burn the chicken coal black and when i complained and asked them to redo it cuz its too burnt they took hell of a time to prepare another burger and it was again burnt black. I think they just gave the same burger and pretended they r making another new one. Making a mistake once is fine but not trying to correct it even after complaining is unforgivable \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Hate this Kohuwala branch. Their food sux, service sux, attitude sux (dnt knw how to talk to customers) and NOT clean. Read up on the tips at foursquare to see just how crappy they are \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Yep, definitely Food Poisoning\u2026. Each and everytime\u2026.", "\r\nSpecially the slow moving items.\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    YOU CALL THAT A SANDWICH, BY THE LOOKS OF IT, THE BREAD IS ALREADY STALE, AND LOOK AT THE AMOUNT OF CHIPS.\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Stick to the subs- they are really tasty. ", "\r\nTry not to dine-in.\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Very poor delivery service.  Not only they got 40 min late to deliver my food but asked me to pay for parking which they did not inform me at the time of ordering. Otherwise I had to go all the way down to collect my order. And the delivery guy was very rude and did not even apologies. \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Food rated 5/5. Quality for the price that is being paid. \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Admittedly it is quite small, but it is supposed to be a takeaway spot and the overall atmosphere after the recent renovation is not too bad.", "\n\n                                            "], "contact": "Call 115 234 291", "address": "Kohuwala, Nugegoda ", "directions": "\n                ", "opening_days": ["MONDAY", "TUESDAY", "WEDNESDAY", "THURSDAY", "FRIDAY", "SATURDAY", "SUNDAY"], "opening_hours": ["11:00 AM \u2013 11:00 PM", "11:00 AM \u2013 11:00 PM", "11:00 AM \u2013 11:00 PM", "11:00 AM \u2013 11:00 PM", "11:00 AM \u2013 11:00 PM", "11:00 AM \u2013 11:00 PM", "11:00 AM \u2013 11:00 PM"], "cuisine": ["Western", "Sri Lankan", "Sri Lankan Chinese", "Fast Food"], "price_range": "Between Rs. 200 - Rs. 500", "dishes": ["Biriyani", "Rice And Curry", "Fried Rice", "Burgers", "Submarines", "Shawarma", "Milkshakes"], "overall_rating": "4", "quality_rating": "4", "service_rating": "3", "ambience_rating": "2", "near_by_places_names": ["Big Bite Biryani", "Vijitha Yapa Bookshop (Nugegoda)", "Gihans Family Restaurant", "Feng Shui Collection", "Mallika Hemachandra Jewellers"], "near_by_places_addresses": ["124, S De S Jayasinghe Road, Kohuwala. ", " 99, S De S Jayasinghe Mawatha, Nugegoda", "68, S De S. Jayasinghe Road, Kohuwala Dehiwala, Colombo", "29A S De S Jayasinghe Mawatha, Dehiwala", "153, S De S. Jayasinghe Mawatha, Nugegoda"], "near_by_places_distances": [" 37 m away", " 151 m away", " 213 m away", " 215 m away", " 237 m away"], "similar_places": ["Dinemore (Marine Drive) ", "Dinemore (Kandy)"]}
{"url": "https://www.yamu.lk/place/burgers-hut/review-49328", "name": "Burgers Hut", "excerpt": "Burger's Hut in Dehiwala was the first of the Burger's King clones, but a good one at that. We dropped in again after a while and we're happy to see that their burgers are still tasty and cheap. Unlike Burger's King though, BH is open from 1 pm.", "yamu_review": ["Burger's Hut in Dehiwala was the first of the Burger's King clones, and a good one at that. We dropped in again after a while and we're happy to see that their burgers are still tasty and relatively cheap. Unlike Burger's King though, BH is open from 1 PM.", "The Burgers Hut menu is basically Burger's King in Dehiwala. They now also offer fried chicken in the form of drumlets, wings and nuggets. Note that a majority of their burger options are chicken-based. All their burgers are priced under Rs. 350, which is great value for money since they're all pretty sizeable and come with a side of fries.", "We've heard good things about their chicken cordon bleu (Rs. 360) and we can confirm that the hype is legit. While the price has gone up by Rs. 100 since 2013, the quality hasn't taken a hit. We recently tried out the cordon bleu at ", ", and this one is comparably good in terms of flavour, with a larger patty to boot. Just like the former, you get a roasted chicken breast with melted cheese in the center, which oozes out as you bite into the burger.", "While they seem to favor chicken burgers, they do offer a few beef and fish options as well. The beef steak burger (Rs. 260), while not completely accurate in terms of description, turned out to be a pleasant surprise. What you get in reality is a patty which tastes and looks very much like a thick slice of roast beef pepperoni topped with a (un)healthy dose of melted cheese, which we totally aren't complaining about. While it's certianly not a \"beef steak\", it was still quite tasty with a slight spiciness to it as well.", "We've also tried their crispy chicken burger (Rs. 300) on our previous visit and it was a winner. Quite simply put, it's a massive fillet of fried chicken which was in fact crispy and gladly not overcooked.", "Burger's Hut is a small roadside eatery in Dehiwala on Allen Avenue. It's more or a less the hole in the wall equivalent of burger spots. They do have a small seating area which is clean enough to have a quick bite but taken away is what you should be looking at.", "Unlike Burger's King, BH is a much smaller operation handle by a few dudes. We haven't really been here at a very busy time but they're friendly and the service is fast, plus they accept Visa and Amex cards.", "While they aren't really competing, Burger's Hut has proven itself worthy of the \"Burger's\" prefix. While their location isn't the most accessible, their burgers are still offer value for money while not compromising on portions and flavour.", "\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                    Burger's Hut in Dehiwala was the first of the Burger's King clones, but a good one at that. We dropped in again after a while and we're happy to see that their burgers are still tasty and cheap. Unlike Burger's King though, BH is open from 1 pm.\n                                                                                                                            ", "\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                    Burger's Hut is a new(ish) burger joint in Dehiwala run by a small group of Burger's King defectors; (almost the) same thing, different location.\n                                                                                                                            ", "\n                                                                                                                                    ", "\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                    \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dbd \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dab\u0da7, \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db8 \u0dbb\u0dc3\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbb\u0dca \u0d9a\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db4\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db1\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc4\u0da7\u0dca \u0d91\u0d9a \u0dc4\u0db3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db4\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca.\n                                                                                                                            ", "\n                                                                                                                                    ", "\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                    \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dda \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db6\u0da9\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dab\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbb\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd1\u0daf\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0db8\u0dda \u0d85\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd1\u0db1\u0dd9 \u0d85\u0db4\u0dda. \u0d9a\u0da9\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d91\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd2 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0d9c\u0dd9 \u0d9a\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0d86\u0dba\u0dd9 \u0db6\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbb\u0dca \u0d9a\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d91\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd9 \u0d9a\u0dc0\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dbd. \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf \u0db1\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2.\n                                                                                                                            ", "\n                                                                                                                                    ", "\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                    \u0db6\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc4\u0da7\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dbd \u0d9c\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbd \u0dc4\u0d82\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dbd \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd8\u0dad \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1 \u0dbd\u0daf \u200d\u0db6\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbb\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dd2. \u0d91\u0dba \u0db4\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dda \u0db6\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0d82\u0dc4\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dbb \u0d89\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0d9a\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dcf\u0dba\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2. \u0d91\u0dc4\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc2\u0dca\u0db4\u0dcf\u0daf\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0d82\u0dc4\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc2\u0dca\u0db4\u0dcf\u0daf\u0db1 \u0dc0\u0d9c\u0dda\u0db8\u0dba. \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc3 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0db8\u0dab\u0dd2. \n                                                                                                                            "], "user_reviews": ["\n                                            ", "\n                                    ", "\n                                            Still one of best burger \n                                    ", "\n                                            Reasonable price,tasty,simple,fast\u2026but little bit salty (as my tongue indonesian)\n                                    "], "user_comments": ["\n\n                                    Real value for money :) The Shawarma's are also pretty good. \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    I live close by and have been visiting the place quite often\u2026 I find it better than than Burger's King\u2026 :)", "\r\nShay\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Burger's king you have been a good friend\u2026\u2026\u2026 :P but it's time to say good bye :(\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Burger's King was a defector of Dine-more \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Burger's Hut has better bread than the dry ones at burger's king! try the no.1 on the menu (crispy chicken burger), it's similar to snackers at KFC but better with some garlic sauce:)", "\r\nlike their page: ", " \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Great food indeed.", "\r\n\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Excellent stuff. Crispy chicken burger is my favorite\u2026 The filled grilled chicken Shawarma is also wonderful\u2026 It's really worth for what we spend\u2026 Keep it up & good luck.\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    too much of sauce\u2026\u2026.", "\r\n\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    awesome food\u2026.agree with saaaaa\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026too much sauce\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    place is great, but DO NOT buy the submarine. worse than burger's king's\u2026\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    The foods goods / better variety than burgers king and the standards at BK has drastically dropped. worthe the money ", "\r\n\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Been there a couple of times but found the buns very dry  and oldish on both occasions. Must be just my luck. The meats though are well marinated and fulfilling. I miss the mutton curry bun Burgers King used to have and was hoping that Burgers Hut would have it, but they dont :(\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    The best here is the shawarma", "\r\n\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    tried it and loved it its real value for money", "\r\n\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    please don`t go in a vehicle boz i went there on my car and buger`s hut staff fight with some others and my car got damaged bu no one is responsible for that. from that i never go there\u2026.", "\r\n\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Burgers are good but more for a snack than a meal.\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Chicken Sawarma is the best.", "\n\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    I never recomnd anyone to visit.i post a comment to theres fb page they delet that and block me.what a respond\u2026no quality at all.submarine is worst\u2026\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    I love this place\u2026Gordon Bleus, the Chicken Gammon Steak Burger and the grilled Beef burger are just moreish\u2026Hands down the best Burger joint I've been to ever since I moved to Sri Lanka. Worth every cent you spend! \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    I tried this place for 3 times during last week\u2026 They are so disappointing\u2026 the quality has gone down dramatically :-(\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Yummy\u2026  Reasonable prices.\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Yamu it's says \"bacon\" in ur review is that correct or typo???? Plz respond asap\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Hey Concerned, it's just chicken-bacon at Burger's Hut. \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    we enjoined \n                                            ", "\n\n                                    The Cashier in Burgers Hut is really nice. Once my bill came to around Rs.545. I gave him a Rs.1000 note and since he didnt have any change in the register he returned Rs.500 back to me without hesitating. His name tag read Aqib Aslam. Hospitality wise i was really impressed. The food portions were pretty decent aswell. Definitely going back.\n                                            ", "\n\n                                    Where's my comment mate\u2026it's  not here yet.why ?\n                                            "], "contact": "Call 0773669667", "address": "Allen Avenue, Dehiwala (Opposite Nawalanka Food City) ", "directions": "From Galle Road you can turn up from the William Grinding Mill Junction, then take your first major right. It's about 300m up the road, across from a grocery store. You can also come from the Karagampitiya side, it's about 1km after the Zoo.", "opening_days": ["MONDAY", "TUESDAY", "WEDNESDAY", "THURSDAY", "FRIDAY", "SATURDAY", "SUNDAY"], "opening_hours": ["01:00 PM \u2013 11:00 PM", "01:00 PM \u2013 11:00 PM", "01:00 PM \u2013 11:00 PM", "01:00 PM \u2013 11:00 PM", "01:00 PM \u2013 11:00 PM", "01:00 PM \u2013 11:00 PM", "01:00 PM \u2013 11:00 PM"], "cuisine": ["Between Rs. 200 - Rs. 500"], "price_range": "Beef"