{"url": "https://www.yamu.lk/place/meal-centre/review-9389", "name": "Meal Centre", "excerpt": "Clean, tidy and located on the side of the road with a broad car park, you can spot Damith from afar by its curling yellow logo. A welcome change from the abundance of Wonder Bakeries - really not so wonderful - Damith provides honest, tasty Sri Lankan food.", "yamu_review": ["\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                    Clean, tidy and located on the side of the road with a broad car park, you can spot Damith from afar by its curling yellow logo. A welcome change from the abundance of Wonder Bakeries - really not so wonderful - Damith provides honest, tasty Sri Lankan food.\n                                                                                                                            ", "\n                                                                                                                                    ", "\n                                                                \n                                                                                                                                    \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dda \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0daf\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dba\u0dd2. \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2. \u0db4\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db4\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d91\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0dad\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf. \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba\u0db8\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0daf\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dba\u0dd2. \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc1\u0dd3\u0dbd\u0dd3\u0dba\u0